room_title: Escape room "Jumanji VR" by The Void Las Vegas in Las Vegas
room_address: 3377 S Las Vegas Blvd #2235 Las Vegas, NV 89109
room_description: The evil Haka’ar has stolen the Scepter of Se’payu containing the Red Jewel of Jumanji! You and your companions must enter the game, take on the form of its heroes and stop Haka’ar from remaking the world into his own! Only you can save Jumanji!
